-- Arabtec to float 40 pct of construction business on Abu Dhabi bourse - CEO
-- By Stanley Carvalho
-- Wed Apr 30, 2014 07:08AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, April 30 (Reuters) - Dubai builder Arabtec's <ARTC.DU> Chief Executive Hasan Ismaik said on Wednesday that the company will spin off and float 40 percent of its construction business in an initial public offering on the Abu Dhabi bourse slated for 2015.

